<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>15 reveladoras estadísticas de las compras online para 2020</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/es/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Online Shopping Statistics [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-115244" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/Online-Shopping-Statistics-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5fd098efed8ba" class="block-preamble"><p>Fue <a href="https://money.com/online-shopping-history-anniversary/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">hace más de 25 años</a> (1994) cuando se realizó la primera compra online documentada.</p>
</div>






<p>Desde entonces, las compras online han crecido desde ser un concepto nuevo a ser una industria de billones de dólares.</p>



<p>Para ponerlo en perspectiva y tener una visión del estado actual de las cosas, he compilado una lista de algunas de las estadísticas de compras online más reveladoras de 2020.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Estas te mostrarán dónde está actualmente la industria, a dónde se dirige y qué puedes hacer para que tu tienda sea más competitiva.</p>



<p>Comencemos.</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5ea163cd21ab2" class="block-content-upgrade">
