<h2><strong>Índice de contenido</strong></h2>



<p><a href="#1">1. Se espera que las ventas de e-commerce alcancen los $4.2 billones para finales de 2020 (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#2">2. Se predice que las ventas de e-commerce lleguen a $6.5 billones para 2023 (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#3">3. Hay 2.05 mil millones de compradores online en 2020 (Oberlo)</a></p>



<p><a href="#4">4. 75 por ciento de las personas compran online al menos una vez al mes (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#5">5. 63 por ciento de los caminos de compra comienzan online (Think with Google)</a></p>



<p><a href="#6">6. Casi la mitad (49.2 por ciento) de las ventas de e-commerce se hacen a través de dispositivos móviles en 2020 (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#7">7. Para 2021, el 53.9 por ciento de las ventas de e-commerce se harán a través de dispositivos móviles (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#8">8. Amazon tiene el 47 por ciento de todas las ventas de e-commerce de Estados Unidos en 2020 (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#9">9. Amazon tendrá el 50 por ciento de todas las ventas de e-commerce de Estados Unidos en 2021 (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#10">10. 80 por ciento de los compradores online, y 63 por ciento de los compradores móviles, piensan que las nuevas tecnologías e innovaciones mejoran su experiencia (National Retail Federation)</a></p>



<p><a href="#11">11. La búsqueda y la navegación son los elementos más importantes de un sitio para los compradores online (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#12">12. Tener calificaciones y reseñas es el segundo elemento más importante (Statista)</a></p>



<p><a href="#13">13. Los costos extra son la razón número uno del abandono de carrito (Baymard Institute)</a></p>



<p><a href="#14">14. Forzar a los compradores a crear una cuenta es la razón número dos del abandono de carrito (Baymard Institute)</a></p>



<p><a href="#15">15. Reorientar a los visitantes de un sitio web hace que sea 43 por ciento más probable que compren (PR Newswire)</a></p>



<h2 id="1">1. Se espera que las ventas de e-commerce alcancen los $4.2 billones para finales de 2020 (Statista)</h2>



<p>Ha habido un crecimiento significativo del e-commerce en años recientes. En 2014, las ventas totales llegaron a apenas <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/379046/worldwide-retail-e-commerce-sales/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">$1.3 billones</a>. </p>



<p>Pero ese número se ha más que triplicado en 2020 a $4.2 billones, y se anticipa que siga creciendo a medida que avancemos en la década de los 2020.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="790" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1024x790.png" alt="1 Retail e-commerce" class="wp-image-115160" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1024x790.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-300x231.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-768x593.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1536x1185.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-380x293.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-600x463.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-760x586.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-1440x1111.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-45x35.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-65x50.png 65w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-635x490.png 635w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-220x170.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce-385x297.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/1-Retail-e-commerce.png 1664w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h2 id="2">2. Se predice que las ventas de e-commerce lleguen a $6.5 billones para 2023 (Statista)</h2>



<p>De hecho, los expertos han proyectado un ingreso anual que subirá hasta los <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/379046/worldwide-retail-e-commerce-sales/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">$6.5 billones</a> en apenas tres años. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="805" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1024x805.png" alt="2 Retail Worldwide" class="wp-image-115161" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1024x805.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-300x236.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-768x604.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1536x1208.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-380x299.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-600x472.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-760x598.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-1440x1132.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-45x35.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-64x50.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-623x490.png 623w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-220x173.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide-385x303.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/2-Retail-Worldwide.png 1638w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Si esta tendencia mantiene su trayectoria, las ventas de e-commerce pudieran, potencialmente, alcanzar los $8 billones al año para el 2025.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Esta es una noticia excelente para las marcas digitales, y muestra cuánta oportunidad hay en el mercado.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Aunque, ciertamente, incrementará el número de competidores, también aumentarán las ganancias.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Así que ahora es el momento perfecto para subir a bordo.&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="3">3. Hay 2.05 mil millones de compradores online en 2020 (Oberlo)</h2>



<p>Para 2020, hay aproximadamente <a href="https://www.worldometers.info/world-population/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">7.8 mil millones</a> de personas en el mundo. Y poco más de un cuarto (<a href="https://www.oberlo.com/statistics/how-many-people-shop-online" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">26.28 por ciento</a>) de ellos son compradores online. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="524" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1024x524.png" alt="3 Oberlo" class="wp-image-115162" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1024x524.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-300x153.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-768x393.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1536x785.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-380x194.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-600x307.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-760x389.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-1440x736.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-68x35.png 68w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-98x50.png 98w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-740x378.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-220x113.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo-385x197.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/3-Oberlo.png 1760w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Como puedes ver, ha habido un aumento considerable en el número de compradores digitales con el pasar de los años, pues ha pasado de 1.32 mil millones en 2014 a 2.05 mil millones en 2020.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Con más y más personas comprando de forma digital, las marcas de e-commerce tienen la oportunidad de llegar a una audiencia masiva.&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="4">4. 75 por ciento de las personas compran online al menos una vez al mes (Statista)</h2>



<p>También vale la pena destacar que la gran mayoría de personas que compran online, lo hacen frecuentemente.&nbsp;</p>



<p>La investigación de <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/664770/online-shopping-frequency-worldwide/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Statista</a> determinó que:</p>



<ul><li>20 por ciento compran online una vez a la semana</li><li>24 por ciento compran online cada dos semanas</li><li>31 por ciento compran online una vez al mes</li></ul>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="718" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1024x718.png" alt="4 Additional Information" class="wp-image-115163" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1024x718.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-300x210.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-768x539.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1536x1077.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-380x267.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-600x421.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-760x533.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-1440x1010.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-50x35.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-71x50.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-699x490.png 699w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-220x154.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information-385x270.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/4-Additional-Information.png 1628w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>En comparación, un número mucho menor (15 por ciento) compra 3-4 veces por trimestre, y solo 10 por ciento compra una vez cada tres meses.&nbsp;</p>



<p>El punto es que las compras online se están convirtiendo en la norma, y hay grandes oportunidades de lograr clientes recurrentes que te comprarán una y otra vez.&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="5">5. 63 por ciento de los caminos de compra comienzan online (Think with Google)</h2>



<p>Una de las estadísticas de compras online más interesantes es que más de seis de cada 10 caminos de compra comienzan online (<a href="https://www.thinkwithgoogle.com/feature/path-to-purchase-search-behavior/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">fuente</a>).</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="917" height="1024" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-917x1024.png" alt="5 Percentage Circle" class="wp-image-115164" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-917x1024.png 917w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-269x300.png 269w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-768x857.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-380x424.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-600x670.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-760x848.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-31x35.png 31w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-45x50.png 45w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-439x490.png 439w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-220x246.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle-385x430.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/5-Percentage-Circle.png 1014w" sizes="(max-width: 917px) 100vw, 917px" /></figure></div>



<p>Independientemente de si la persona termina comprando en una tienda de e-commerce o en una tienda física tradicional, la mayor parte de la investigación inicial comienza en el mundo digital.</p>



<p>“Es por esto que es extremadamente importante que las marcas tengan una fuerte presencia online”, explica <a href="https://www.oberlo.com/blog/online-shopping-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Maryam Moshin</a>, escritora especializada en e-commerce y dropshipping.</p>



<p>“Al mejorar la experiencia del cliente desde el primer paso, las empresas tienen más probabilidades de hacer que los clientes compren en su tienda”.</p>



<p>Por ende, es inteligente invertir en estrategias de marketing digital, como SEO y redes sociales.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Las marcas que lo hacen pueden generar un alto volumen de leads y desarrollar una equidad de marca que pueda rendir frutos cuando los compradores estén decidiendo en dónde comprar.</p>



<p>Por ejemplo, la compañía de exfoliantes <a href="https://www.frankbody.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Frank Body</a> tiene, actualmente, 745.000 seguidores en Instagram, algo que influye fuertemente en su exposición de marca y su éxito.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="461" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1024x461.png" alt="6 Frank Body" class="wp-image-115165" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1024x461.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-300x135.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-768x346.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1536x692.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-380x171.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-600x270.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-760x342.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-1440x648.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-78x35.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-111x50.png 111w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-740x333.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-220x99.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body-385x173.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/6-Frank-Body.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/frank_bod/?hl=en"></a></p>



<h2 id="6">6. Casi la mitad (49.2 por ciento) de las ventas de e-commerce se hacen a través de dispositivos móviles en 2020 (Statista)</h2>



<p>Los compradores online que hacen compras a través de dispositivos móviles no son nada nuevo. Pero se han incrementado en casi <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/249863/us-mobile-retail-commerce-sales-as-percentage-of-e-commerce-sales/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">15 por ciento</a> en los últimos cuatro años.</p>



<p>En 2017, solo 34.5 por ciento de las ventas de e-commerce se hicieron a través de dispositivos móviles, pero la cifra está en casi 50 por ciento en 2020.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="703" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1024x703.png" alt="7 Column four" class="wp-image-115167" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1024x703.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-300x206.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-768x527.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1536x1054.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-380x261.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-600x412.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-760x522.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-1440x989.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-51x35.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-73x50.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-714x490.png 714w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-220x151.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four-385x264.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/7-Column-four.png 1646w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h2 id="7">7. Para 2021, el 53.9 por ciento de las ventas de e-commerce se harán a través de dispositivos móviles (Statista)</h2>



<p>Y 2021 debería marcar el punto crucial en el que se harán más ventas a través de dispositivos móviles que desde computadoras de escritorio y laptops (<a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/249863/us-mobile-retail-commerce-sales-as-percentage-of-e-commerce-sales/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">fuente</a>).</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="713" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1024x713.png" alt="8 Column five" class="wp-image-115169" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1024x713.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-300x209.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-768x535.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1536x1070.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-380x265.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-600x418.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-760x529.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-1440x1003.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-50x35.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-72x50.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-703x490.png 703w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-220x153.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five-385x268.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/8-Column-five.png 1628w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Esto muestra la importancia de optimizar para móviles y proporcionarle a este segmento de visitantes una experiencia de compra sin inconvenientes&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="8">8. Amazon tiene el 47 por ciento de todas las ventas de e-commerce de Estados Unidos en 2020 (Statista)</h2>



<p>Probablemente no necesito señalar que Amazon es un gigante del e-commerce que posee un porcentaje masivo del mercado.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Pero su poder realmente se ha incrementado en los últimos años, cuando pasaron de tener el <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/788109/amazon-retail-market-share-usa/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">34 por ciento</a> de las ventas de e-commerce en Estados Unidos en 2016, al 47 por ciento en 2020. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="722" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1024x722.png" alt="9 column four" class="wp-image-115171" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1024x722.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-300x211.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-768x541.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1536x1083.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-380x268.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-600x423.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-760x536.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-1440x1015.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-50x35.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-71x50.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-695x490.png 695w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-220x155.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four-385x271.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/9-column-four.png 1620w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h2 id="9">9. Amazon tendrá el 50 por ciento de todas las ventas de e-commerce de Estados Unidos en 2021 (Statista)</h2>



<p>Y, para el 2021, tienen proyectado representar oficialmente la mitad de todas las ventas de e-commerce en Estados Unidos (<a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/788109/amazon-retail-market-share-usa/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">fuente</a>).</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="710" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1024x710.png" alt="10 column 5" class="wp-image-115173" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1024x710.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-300x208.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-768x532.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1536x1065.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-380x263.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-600x416.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-760x527.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-1440x998.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-50x35.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-72x50.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-707x490.png 707w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-220x153.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5-385x267.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/10-column-5.png 1624w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Aunque últimamente Amazon ha estado bajo una cantidad considerable de escrutinio y críticas, es imposible negar su presencia en las compras online.</p>



<p>Aparentemente abarcan todo, desde libros hasta electrónicos, y desde comestibles hasta streaming de música. No digo esto para asustar o desmotivar a las marcas pequeñas de e-commerce.</p>



<p>Pero, definitivamente, es algo que debes tener en cuenta, y es vital desarrollar una estrategia realista que te permita competir con Amazon.</p>



<h2 id="10">10. 80 por ciento de los compradores online, y 63 por ciento de los compradores móviles, piensan que las nuevas tecnologías e innovaciones mejoran su experiencia (National Retail Federation)</h2>



<p>Dado que la base en sí de las compras online es la tecnología de vanguardia, no debería ser una sorpresa que estos compradores sean fanáticos de las nuevas tecnologías e innovaciones (<a href="https://nrf.com/research/consumer-view-summer-2019" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">fuente</a>).</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="457" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1024x457.png" alt="11 percent circles" class="wp-image-115175" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1024x457.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-300x134.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-768x343.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1536x686.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-380x170.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-600x268.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-760x339.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-1440x643.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-78x35.png 78w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-112x50.png 112w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-740x330.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-220x98.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles-385x172.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/11-percent-circles.png 1904w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://towardsdatascience.com/top-12-ways-ai-is-revolutionizing-the-online-shopping-ecommerce-trends-9c3e98ef519c" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Sophia Martin</a>, tech lead y escritora en Xicom.biz, ofrece algunos ejemplos, como:</p>



<ul><li>IA que proporciona soporte al cliente 24/7.</li><li>Chatbots que proporcionan soluciones instantáneas para prácticamente cualquier problema que los compradores puedan tener.</li><li>Aprendizaje automatizado para ofrecer mensajería personalizada.</li><li>Recomendaciones de productos basadas en historial previo de compras, preferencias, ubicación, etc.</li></ul>



<p>Este es un ejemplo de <a href="https://us.pandora.net/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Pandora</a>, una compañía danesa de joyas, usando recomendaciones de productos para ayudar a los compradores a descubrir otros productos que les pudieran interesar. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="534" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1024x534.jpg" alt="12 Pandora" class="wp-image-115177" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-1024x534.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-300x157.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-768x401.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-380x198.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-600x313.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-760x396.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-67x35.jpg 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-96x50.jpg 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-740x386.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-220x115.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora-385x201.jpg 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/12-Pandora.jpg 1200w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Y esa es solo la punta del iceberg. Las tecnologías como estas avanzan rápidamente y evolucionan todo el tiempo.</p>



<p>Mantenerse al día con lo que pasa y experimentar continuamente puede ayudar a tu marca de e-commerce a ofrecer una experiencia de cliente mucho mejor y mantenerse competitiva.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Así que esto es algo que, definitivamente, quieres aprovechar.&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="11">11. La búsqueda y la navegación son los elementos más importantes de un sitio para los compradores online (Statista)</h2>



<p>Datos recientes indican que hacer que los productos sean fáciles de encontrar a través de una búsqueda y navegación simples, fue el atributo más importante para la experiencia de compra online para <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/973413/most-important-attributes-online-shopping-shoppers-usa/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">61 por ciento</a> de los compradores. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="727" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1024x727.png" alt="13 vertical stat" class="wp-image-115179" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1024x727.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-300x213.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-768x545.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1536x1091.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-380x270.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-600x426.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-760x540.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-1440x1022.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-49x35.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-70x50.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-690x490.png 690w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-220x156.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat-385x273.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/13-vertical-stat.png 1614w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Y esto tiene sentido. Después de todo, ¿quién quiere tener dificultades para encontrar lo que busca?</p>



<p>Es por eso que debes priorizar la búsqueda y la navegación, y hacer un esfuerzo constante para hacer mejoras continuas, incluso si solo son mínimas.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Un buen ejemplo de una marca con una navegación extremadamente sencilla es la compañía de calzado <a href="https://www.rollienation.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Rollie Nation</a>.</p>



<p>Inmediatamente después de aterrizar en su sitio, los compradores encuentran un menú de navegación simple y directo.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="497" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1024x497.png" alt="14 Aura Bar" class="wp-image-115186" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1024x497.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-768x373.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1536x746.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-760x369.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-1440x699.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-740x359.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/14-Aura-Bar.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Con un rápido clic en una categoría, pueden especificar sin problemas su búsqueda.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="497" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category-1024x497.png" alt="15 Women Category" class="wp-image-115191" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category-1024x497.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category-768x373.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category-1536x745.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category-760x369.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category-1440x699.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category-740x359.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/15-Women-Category.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="496" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes-1024x496.png" alt="16 Shoes" class="wp-image-115196" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes-1024x496.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes-768x372.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes-1536x744.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes-760x368.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes-1440x697.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes-740x358.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes-385x186.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/16-Shoes.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Y también hay una función de búsqueda colocada intuitivamente para mayor conveniencia.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="495" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1024x495.png" alt="17 Search" class="wp-image-115203" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1024x495.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-768x371.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1536x742.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-600x290.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-760x367.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-1440x696.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-740x358.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search-385x186.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/17-Search.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="495" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1024x495.png" alt="18 Looking for" class="wp-image-115209" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1024x495.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-768x372.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1536x743.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-600x290.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-760x368.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-1440x697.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-740x358.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for-385x186.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/18-Looking-for.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Menos esfuerzo para los visitantes se traduce en que pueden encontrar los productos que quieren sin ningún drama, y esto incrementa sus probabilidades de compra.&nbsp;</p>



<h2 id="12">12. Tener calificaciones y reseñas es el segundo elemento más importante (Statista)</h2>



<p>Comprar online es algo divertido y emocionante, pero también puede ser abrumador, algunas veces.&nbsp;</p>



<p>A menudo, los compradores tienen que filtrar a través de montones de productos diferentes para encontrar lo que buscan, y todas las opciones pueden dejarlos sintiéndose un poco paralizados.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Una de las mejores formas de aumentar la confianza del comprador y darle la información que necesita, es ofreciéndole acceso a calificaciones y reseñas de los productos.&nbsp;</p>



<p>De hecho, ese es el atributo más importante de una experiencia de compra online para <a href="https://www.statista.com/statistics/973413/most-important-attributes-online-shopping-shoppers-usa/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">53 por ciento</a> de las personas. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="697" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1024x697.png" alt="19 Top percent" class="wp-image-115210" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1024x697.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-300x204.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-768x523.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1536x1046.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-380x259.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-600x409.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-760x518.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-1440x981.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-51x35.png 51w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-73x50.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-720x490.png 720w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-220x150.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent-385x262.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/19-Top-percent.png 1636w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Incluso pudiéramos apuntar que tener esta información lista y disponible ha sido una gran parte del éxito de Amazon.</p>



<p>Después de todo, hacen que sea extremadamente fácil encontrar las calificaciones de los productos que venden, así como reseñas exhaustivas de los clientes.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="499" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1024x499.png" alt="20 customer review" class="wp-image-115213" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1024x499.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-768x374.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1536x748.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-600x292.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-760x370.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-1440x702.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-740x361.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review-385x188.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/20-customer-review.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Y es una buena idea para todas las marcas de e-commerce ofrecer esto, también.</p>



<p>Eso es lo que hace <a href="https://www.blissworld.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Bliss</a>, una compañía de productos para el cuidado de la piel. </p>



<p>Mira lo que los compradores pueden encontrar en su producto “Bright Idea Moisturizer”.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="487" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-1024x487.png" alt="21 Bliss" class="wp-image-115216" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-1024x487.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-768x365.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-1536x731.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-600x285.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-760x362.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-1440x685.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-74x35.png 74w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-740x352.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss-385x183.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/21-Bliss.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Estas son reseñas.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="444" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews-1024x444.png" alt="22 Reviews" class="wp-image-115219" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews-1024x444.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews-300x130.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews-768x333.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews-1536x666.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews-380x165.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews-600x260.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews-760x330.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews-1440x625.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews-81x35.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews-115x50.png 115w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews-740x321.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews-220x95.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews-385x167.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/22-Reviews.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Y también hay una calificación para que los compradores puedan tomar una decisión bien informada y usar la sabiduría popular para determinar el nivel de calidad.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="443" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews-1024x443.png" alt="23 Score Reviews" class="wp-image-115221" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews-1024x443.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews-300x130.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews-768x332.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews-1536x665.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews-380x164.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews-600x260.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews-760x329.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews-1440x623.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews-81x35.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews-116x50.png 116w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews-740x320.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews-220x95.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews-385x167.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/23-Score-Reviews.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h2 id="13">13. Los costos extra son la razón número uno del abandono de carrito (Baymard Institute)</h2>



<p>Una alta <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/cart-abandonment-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">tasa de abandono del carrito</a> de compra puede ser uno de los más grandes obstáculos para crear una tienda de e-commerce exitosa.</p>



<p>Así que es esencial que sepas cómo mantener esto a raya y conozcas las razones específicas por las que los compradores no completan sus compras.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Si bien existen varias razones para el abandono del carrito durante el proceso de pago, los costos extra como envío, impuestos y comisiones son, por mucho, las principales causas.</p>



<p>De hecho, la mitad de todos los compradores se han ido durante el proceso de pago debido a esto (<a href="https://baymard.com/lists/cart-abandonment-rate" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">fuente</a>).</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="724" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1024x724.png" alt="24 Top statistics" class="wp-image-115223" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1024x724.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-300x212.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-768x543.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1536x1085.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-380x268.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-600x424.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-760x537.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-1440x1017.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-50x35.png 50w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-71x50.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-693x490.png 693w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-220x155.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics-385x272.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/24-Top-statistics.png 1888w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Es por eso que es importante ser transparente sobre estos costos, y ofrecer envíos gratis cada vez que sea posible.&nbsp;</p>



<p>La marca de ropa moderna <a href="https://www.mycentsofstyle.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Cents of Style</a>, por ejemplo, ofrece siempre envíos gratis y se los dice a los compradores tan pronto como llegan a su sitio.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="501" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1024x501.png" alt="25 Scents of Style" class="wp-image-115227" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1024x501.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-300x147.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-768x376.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1536x751.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-380x186.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-600x294.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-760x372.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-1440x705.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-102x50.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-740x362.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style-385x188.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/25-Scents-of-Style.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h2 id="14">14. Forzar a los compradores a crear una cuenta es la razón número dos del abandono de carrito (Baymard Institute)</h2>



<p>La investigación halló que <a href="https://baymard.com/lists/cart-abandonment-rate" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">28 por ciento</a> de los compradores no han completado una compra porque se les pidió que crearan una cuenta. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="729" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1024x729.png" alt="26 Abandonment reasons" class="wp-image-115231" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1024x729.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-300x214.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-768x547.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1536x1093.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-380x270.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-600x427.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-760x541.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-1440x1025.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-49x35.png 49w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-70x50.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-688x490.png 688w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-220x157.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons-385x274.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/26-Abandonment-reasons.png 1894w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Sé que, personalmente, me fastidia cuando he hecho mi compra online, he añadido los artículos al carrito y tengo todo listo para pagar y, de repente, me golpea la molesta pantalla de “crea una cuenta”.</p>



<p>Aunque no es tanto problema si tengo previsto comprar una y otra vez de esa compañía, sí es un gran fastidio si solo quiero hacer una compra de una sola vez. Y, al parecer, muchas otras personas se sienten igual. Es por eso que sugiero darles a los compradores la opción de usar un proceso de pago para visitantes.</p>



<p>Esto reduce mucho la fricción y les permite a los compradores adquirir sus artículos sin inconvenientes y sin tener que pasar por el proceso de crear una cuenta.</p>



<p>Eso es lo que hace la marca de muebles y decoración del hogar <a href="https://www.crateandbarrel.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Crate and Barrel</a>, y funciona excelentemente. </p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="600" height="345" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel.png" alt="27 Crate &amp; Barrel" class="wp-image-115233" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel-300x173.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel-380x219.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel-61x35.png 61w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel-87x50.png 87w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel-220x127.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/27-Crate-Barrel-385x221.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 600px) 100vw, 600px" /></figure></div>



<h2 id="15">15. Reorientar a los visitantes de un sitio web hace que sea 43 por ciento más probable que compren (PR Newswire)</h2>



<p>Desafortunadamente, no importa cuán grandiosa sea tu tienda de e-commerce, <a href="https://www.prnewswire.com/news-releases/study-92-percent-of-consumers-visiting-a-retailers-website-for-the-first-time-arent-there-to-buy-300390086.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">92 por ciento</a> de los compradores no están listos para comprar de buenas a primeras. </p>



<p>Puede que simplemente están haciendo una investigación inicial, un “mirar vidrieras” virtual, o simplemente todavía no están en esa mentalidad de comprar.</p>



<p>La conclusión es que la mayoría no resultará en una venta la primera vez que aterricen en tu sitio.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Pero eso no significa, necesariamente, que se te hayan escapado de los dedos y se hayan ido para siempre.</p>



<p>Reorientar (retargeting) a los visitantes ha demostrado ser una táctica altamente efectiva para mantener a las marcas de e-commerce dentro del radar de los compradores y, sutilmente, dirigirlos de regreso a los productos en los que mostraron interés.</p>



<p>Por ejemplo, Hawthorne, una compañía que vende artículos de cuidado personal para hombres, usa este ad reorientado en Facebook para captar la atención de visitantes precios y dirigirlos de regreso a su sitio.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="814" height="1024" src="http://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-814x1024.png" alt="28 Hawthorne" class="wp-image-115235" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-814x1024.png 814w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-238x300.png 238w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-768x967.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-380x478.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-600x755.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-760x957.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-28x35.png 28w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-40x50.png 40w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-389x490.png 389w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-220x277.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne-385x485.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/12/28-Hawthorne.png 1044w" sizes="(max-width: 814px) 100vw, 814px" /></figure></div>



<p>“El retargeting les da un empujoncito hacia su marca”, dice el estratega de contenido <a href="https://blog.spiralytics.com/retargeting-statistics" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Pierre de Braux</a>.</p>



<p>“Cuando un cliente potencial mira un ad reorientado, existe un 70 por ciento de probabilidad de que compre tu producto y no el de tu competidor”.</p>



<p>Así que es, definitivamente, una táctica a considerar en 2020 y más allá.&nbsp;</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5ea163cd21ab2" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">RECURSOS GRATUITOS</p>
