										<content:encoded><![CDATA[
<h1 class="has-text-align-center"><strong>12 de los mejores eslóganes y lemas del e-commerce</strong></h1>
<div class="post-content-category"><a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/category/conversion-rate-optimization" rel="category tag">Conversion Rate Optimization</a></div>


<figure class="wp-block-image alignwide size-large"><img width="1024" height="437" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg" alt="Best E-Commerce Taglines [Wordpress]" class="wp-image-113019" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-1024x437.jpg 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-300x128.jpg 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-768x328.jpg 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-1536x656.jpg 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-2048x875.jpg 2048w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-380x162.jpg 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-600x256.jpg 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-760x325.jpg 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-1440x615.jpg 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-960x410.jpg 960w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-82x35.jpg 82w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-117x50.jpg 117w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-740x316.jpg 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-220x94.jpg 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/Best-E-Commerce-Taglines-Wordpress-385x164.jpg 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure>


<div id="preamble-block_5fb65bf9a4b2a" class="block-preamble"><p>Para mediados de 2020, solo en los Estados Unidos había <a href="https://kommandotech.com/statistics/how-many-ecommerce-sites-are-there/" target="_blank" rel="noopener">1.3 millones de empresas de e-commerce</a>.</p>
</div>






<p>Y ese número crece cada día que pasa. Eso significa que el e-commerce, o comercio electrónico, está prosperando y hay muchas oportunidades.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Sin embargo, también significa que la competencia es fuerte. Y por esta competencia, es absolutamente esencial que distingas tu marca de otras en tu industria.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Una de las formas más fundamentales&nbsp; de hacer esto es creando un eslogan o lema memorable para tu e-commerce.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Para este post, voy a&nbsp; resaltar algunos de los mejores eslóganes y lemas de&nbsp; e-commerce de marcas que están teniendo mucho éxito.&nbsp;</p>



<p>De esta forma, puedes tomar una hoja de papel e inspirarte en estos ejemplos y ponerte manos a la obra con tus propios esfuerzos de branding.&nbsp;</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5fa9475b96b81" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">RECURSOS GRATUITOS</p>
