</div>


<h2><strong>Eslóganes vs lemas</strong></h2>



<p>Primero debo explicar algo rápidamente. Los términos eslogan y lema son muy similares y, como resultado, a menudo los usan de forma intercambiable.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Sin embargo, hay que resaltar que existen algunas diferencias sutiles entre eslogan y lema.&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="http://www.businessdictionary.com/definition/slogan.html" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">BusinessDictionary define eslogan</a> como una “frase simple y pegadiza que acompaña un logo o marca, y que encapsula el atractivo del producto o la misión de la firma y hace que sea memorable”.&nbsp;</p>



<p>“Hay cosas que el dinero no puede comprar. Para todo lo demás, existe&nbsp; MasterCard” es un buen ejemplo.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="536" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard.png" alt="1 Mastercard" class="wp-image-112907" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-300x157.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-768x402.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-380x199.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-600x314.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-760x398.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-67x35.png 67w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-96x50.png 96w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-740x387.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-220x115.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/1-Mastercard-385x202.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://penji.co/best-advertising-tactics/"></a></p>



<p>Por otro lado, <a href="https://www.thebalancesmb.com/what-is-a-tagline-4017760" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">The Balance Small Business</a> define un lema como “una frase corta y memorable que se usa en tu marketing. Debe expresar el sentimiento o sensación principal que quieres que la gente asocie con tu marca”.</p>



<p>Piensa, por ejemplo, en “Me encanta”, de McDonald’s.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="780" height="439" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds.png" alt="2 McDonalds" class="wp-image-112911" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds.png 780w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-300x169.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-768x432.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-380x214.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-600x338.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-760x428.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-62x35.png 62w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-89x50.png 89w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-740x416.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-220x124.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/2-McDonalds-385x217.png 385w" sizes="(max-width: 780px) 100vw, 780px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.cbc.ca/radio/undertheinfluence/the-three-word-jingle-that-made-one-company-billions-of-dollars-1.4598645"></a></p>



<p>Entonces, una de las diferencias principales es el largo: los eslóganes suelen ser más largos que los lemas.</p>



<p>Los eslóganes también tienden a ser un poco más concretos, enfocándose en lo que la marca vende y por qué es beneficioso, mientras que los lemas tienden a ser más abstractos y buscan crear un sentimiento.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Si bien existen unas ligeras diferencias, ambos tienen un objetivo primordial: hacer que la compañía sea más identificable y ayudar a los compradores a asociar una frase con su marca.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Ese es el objetivo por excelencia y es vital para que una empresa sea reconocible y construya una equidad de marca.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Más allá de eso, hay otras semejanzas importantes entre los buenos eslóganes y lemas del e-commerce.&nbsp;</p>



<ul><li>Son simples;</li><li>Son memorables; y</li><li>Crean sentimientos positivos en los compradores.</li></ul>



<h2><strong>12 de los mejores eslóganes y lemas del e-commerce</strong></h2>



<p>Ahora que hemos aclarado todo, dediquémonos al meollo del asunto.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Aquí está un compendio de 12 de los mejores eslóganes y lemas de e-commerces de algunas de las principales marcas de la actualidad, junto con opiniones de qué es lo que los hace tan efectivos.<br><br>Puesto que la mayoría de estos eslóganes y lemas no tienen una versión oficial en español, los he dejado en inglés en sus títulos, y los traduciré en el texto para darte una mejor idea de su significado.</p>



<h2><strong>1. Allbirds: “The World’s Most Comfortable Shoes”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="491" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-1024x491.png" alt="3 Allbirds" class="wp-image-112915" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-1024x491.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-300x144.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-768x368.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-1536x736.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-380x182.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-600x288.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-760x364.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-1440x690.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-740x355.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/3-Allbirds.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.allbirds.com/"><strong></strong></a></p>



<p><a href="https://www.allbirds.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Allbirds</a> es una de mis marcas de zapatillas favoritas, y una compañía que realmente “lo entiende”.</p>



<p>La marca usa materiales naturales para elaborar sus zapatos y tiene un fuerte énfasis en ser ecológicos.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="383" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-1024x383.png" alt="4 Allbirds Sponge" class="wp-image-112919" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-1024x383.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-300x112.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-768x287.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-1536x574.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-380x142.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-600x224.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-760x284.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-1440x538.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-94x35.png 94w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-134x50.png 134w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-740x277.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-220x82.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge-385x144.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/4-Allbirds-Sponge.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.allbirds.com/pages/our-materials-wool"></a></p>



<p>Además de eso, la comodidad es lo que caracteriza a sus zapatos. Así que, ¿qué mejor eslogan que “The World’s Most Comfortable Shoes” (“Los zapatos más cómodos del mundo”)?</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="506" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-1024x506.png" alt="5 Allbirds Shoes" class="wp-image-112923" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-1024x506.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-300x148.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-768x380.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-1536x759.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-380x188.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-600x297.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-760x376.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-1440x712.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-740x366.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes-385x190.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/5-Allbirds-Shoes.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>Lo abarca todo. Es simple, memorable, ayuda a distinguir a Allbirds de sus competidores y genera sentimientos positivos.&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p>Además, activa instantáneamente al interés de muchos compradores. No sé tú, pero la comodidad es enormemente importante para mí cuando tengo que elegir un par de zapatos.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Me siento instantáneamente atraído hacia una marca que me promete los zapatos más cómodos del mundo. Así que podemos aprender mucho de este ejemplo.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>2. Two Chimps Coffee: “Awesome Coffee. No Nonsense.”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="474" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-1024x474.png" alt="6 Two Chimps" class="wp-image-112927" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-1024x474.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-300x139.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-768x355.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-1536x711.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-380x176.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-600x278.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-760x352.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-1440x666.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-108x50.png 108w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-740x342.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps-385x178.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/6-Two-Chimps.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://twochimpscoffee.com/"></a></p>



<p>Esta es una marca de café por suscripción que vende productos recién tostados y cosechados de forma ética.&nbsp;</p>



<p>La marca ha generado mucho revuelo últimamente por su café de alta calidad y su branding inteligente.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="498" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-1024x498.png" alt="7 Two chimps Coffee" class="wp-image-112931" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-1024x498.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-768x374.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-1536x748.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-600x292.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-760x370.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-1440x701.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-740x360.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/7-Two-chimps-Coffee.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://twochimpscoffee.com/"></a></p>



<p>Y una gran parte de eso se debe a su eslogan, “Awesome Coffee. No Nonsense.” (“Café increíble. Sin tonterías.”). Con solo cuatro palabras, <a href="https://twochimpscoffee.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Two Chimps Coffee</a> encapsula perfectamente lo que vende y establece que es algo que vale la pena comprar.&nbsp;</p>



<p>También funciona el que diga que la marca es “sin tonterías”, lo que significa que los compradores no tienen que lidiar con ningún drama o fricción al tratar con Two Chimps Coffee.</p>



<p>En vez de eso, pueden esperar una experiencia profesional y agradable.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>3. Bonobos: “Menswear Founded on Fit, Built on Service, and Focused on Style. However You Fit, Bonobos Fits You.”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="501" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-1024x501.png" alt="8 Bonobos" class="wp-image-112935" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-1024x501.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-300x147.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-768x376.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-1536x752.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-380x186.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-600x294.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-760x372.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-1440x705.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-102x50.png 102w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-740x362.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-220x108.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos-385x189.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/8-Bonobos.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://bonobos.com/"><strong></strong></a></p>



<p>Una traducción aproximada al español sería: “Ropa para hombre basada en un buen ajuste, desarrollada en el servicio y enfocada en el estilo. Sea cual sea tu talla, Bonobos se adapta a ti”. Este es, definitivamente, uno de los eslóganes más largos, con 17 palabras.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>



<p>Pero <a href="https://bonobos.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Bonobos</a> hace un gran trabajo resumiendo lo que vende (ropa para hombres), lo que valoran (un estilo maravilloso) y por qué es una marca con la que vale la pena hacer negocios (tienen productos fantásticos y un excelente servicio al cliente).</p>



<p>Como resultado, es posible atraer a una audiencia y generar algo de interés inicial fuerte.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Una vez que los compradores revisan el sitio de la marca, pueden decir instantáneamente que Bonobos es muy profesional, con una colección extensa de productos para hombres únicos, como estos shorts y camisas en colores pastel.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="493" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-1024x493.png" alt="8 Bonobos" class="wp-image-112939" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-1024x493.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-768x370.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-1536x740.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-380x183.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-600x289.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-760x366.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-1440x694.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-73x35.png 73w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-104x50.png 104w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-740x356.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-220x106.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts-385x185.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/9-Bonobos-shirts.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://bonobos.com/"></a></p>



<p>Todo se basa en poner tu pie en la puerta con tu eslogan o lema, y persuadir a los compradores potenciales para que le den una oportunidad a tu marca.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>4. Lunya: “Sleepwear for the Modern Woman”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="487" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-1024x487.png" alt="10 Lunya" class="wp-image-112943" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-1024x487.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-300x143.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-768x365.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-1536x730.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-380x181.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-600x285.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-760x361.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-1440x684.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-74x35.png 74w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-105x50.png 105w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-740x352.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-220x105.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya-385x183.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/10-Lunya.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.lunya.co/"><strong></strong></a></p>



<p>Al igual que Allbirds y Two Chimps Coffee, <a href="https://www.lunya.co/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Lunya</a> explica de forma concisa lo que venden usando pocas palabras: “Ropa de dormir para la mujer moderna”.</p>



<p>Y, considerando que sus productos están dirigidos específicamente a la mitad de la población (mujeres), han hecho un trabajo fantástico al incluir esto también en el eslogan de su e-commerce.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Esto garantiza que Lunya despierte el interés de su objetivo demográfico y atraiga a los compradores correctos (o compradoras, en este caso).</p>



<p>Una vez que llegan al sitio web de Lunya, los productos van de la mano con el eslogan de su e-commerce, y las compradoras pueden examinar una buena selección de batas, bragas, máscaras para dormir y más.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="474" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-1024x474.png" alt="11 Lunya Sleepwear" class="wp-image-112947" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-1024x474.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-300x139.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-768x356.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-1536x712.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-380x176.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-600x278.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-760x352.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-1440x667.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-108x50.png 108w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-740x343.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear-385x178.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/11-Lunya-Sleepwear.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.lunya.co/"></a></p>



<p>Así que, a la hora de optar por la simplicidad y ser muy directos, este eslogan lo logra con creces, definitivamente.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>5. Birchbox: “Monthly Beauty and Grooming Subscription Boxes”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="498" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-1024x498.png" alt="12 Birchbox" class="wp-image-112951" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-1024x498.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-768x374.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-1536x748.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-600x292.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-760x370.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-1440x701.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-740x360.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/12-Birchbox.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.birchbox.com/"><strong></strong></a></p>



<p><a href="https://www.birchbox.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Birchbox</a> es uno de los servicios de suscripción online de productos de maquillaje y cuidado de la piel y del cabello más famosos.&nbsp;</p>



<p>La marca ha desarrollado una leal clientela, principalmente debido a su transparencia y al proceso de pedidos simplificado que les ofrece a sus clientes.&nbsp;</p>



<p>El eslogan de este e-commerce, “Monthly Beauty and Grooming Subscription Boxes” (“Cajas de productos de belleza mensuales por suscripción”), es tan directo como puede ser y les hace saber a los compradores rápidamente qué es lo que Birchbox ofrece.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Tras visitar su sitio, Birchbox proporciona un resumen rápido de cómo funciona el proceso, informando a los compradores qué pueden esperar al pedir una caja por suscripción.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="567" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-1024x567.png" alt="13 Birchbox Order" class="wp-image-112955" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-1024x567.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-300x166.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-768x425.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-1536x850.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-380x210.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-600x332.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-760x420.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-1440x797.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-63x35.png 63w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-90x50.png 90w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-740x409.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-220x122.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order-385x213.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/13-Birchbox-Order.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.birchbox.com/"></a></p>



<p>Nuevamente, este ejemplo muestra que los mejores eslóganes y lemas de e-commerce son simples y, de forma concisa, dan información clave que los clientes potenciales deben saber.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>6. Flat Tummy Co: “Cleanse &amp; Debloat or Cut the Cals”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="506" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--1024x506.png" alt="14 Flat Tummy" class="wp-image-112959" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--1024x506.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--300x148.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--768x380.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--1536x759.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--380x188.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--600x297.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--760x376.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--1440x712.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--71x35.png 71w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--740x366.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy--385x190.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/14-Flat-Tummy-.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://flattummyco.com/"></a></p>



<p>Esta es una marca de e-commerce que se especializa en productos de manejo del peso para mujeres, como batidos, tés y paletas, así como ropa fitness y esterillas.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Dado que la marca tiene actualmente 1.7 millones de seguidores en Instagram, ha hecho un gran trabajo conectando con su audiencia central y desarrollando una fuerte comunidad digital.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="557" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-1024x557.png" alt="15 $flat Tummy Insta" class="wp-image-112963" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-1024x557.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-300x163.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-768x418.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-1536x835.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-380x207.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-600x326.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-760x413.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-1440x783.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-64x35.png 64w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-92x50.png 92w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-740x402.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-220x120.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta-385x209.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/15-flat-Tummy-Insta.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/flattummyco/"></a></p>



<p>Como mencioné antes, un primer paso esencial para llegar a este nivel es crear un eslogan o lema de e-commerce que comunique de qué se trata tu marca.&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="https://flattummyco.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Flat Tummy Co</a> logra esto perfectamente con su eslogan&nbsp; “Cleanse &amp; Debloat or Cut the Cals” (“Limpia y desinflama o corta la calorías”).</p>



<p>Con pocas pero útiles palabras, los clientes potenciales saben qué pueden esperar lograr al comprar los productos de Flat Tummy Co, lo que llama la atención de su audiencia central.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>7. Everlane: “Modern Basics. Radical Transparency.”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="455" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-1024x455.png" alt="16 Everlane" class="wp-image-112967" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-1024x455.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-300x133.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-768x342.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-1536x683.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-380x169.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-600x267.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-760x338.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-1440x640.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-79x35.png 79w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-112x50.png 112w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-740x329.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-220x98.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane-385x171.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/16-Everlane.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.everlane.com/"><strong></strong></a></p>



<p><a href="https://www.everlane.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Everlane</a> es una popular tienda de ropa online que ha ganado mucha popularidad en los últimos años. La marca ha desarrollado una grandiosa reputación y, por los momentos, se acerca a un millón de seguidores en Instagram.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="596" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-1024x596.png" alt="17 Everlane Insta" class="wp-image-112971" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-1024x596.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-300x175.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-768x447.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-1536x894.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-380x221.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-600x349.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-760x443.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-1440x838.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-60x35.png 60w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-86x50.png 86w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-740x431.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-220x128.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta-385x224.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/17-Everlane-Insta.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/everlane/"></a></p>



<p>Everlane hace muchas cosas bien, y su eslogan de e-commerce (que se traduce como “Básicos modernos. Transparencia radical”) hace un buen trabajo englobando qué son: una marca que proporciona ropa y accesorios básicos y minimalistas, siendo, a la vez, totalmente transparentes sobre sus valores.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Para aclarar, sus valores son crear ropa usando materiales sostenibles, obtenidos de forma ética.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>8. Girlfriend Collective: “Ethically Made Activewear”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="478" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-1024x478.png" alt="18 GF Collective" class="wp-image-112975" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-1024x478.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-300x140.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-768x358.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-1536x717.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-380x177.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-600x280.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-760x355.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-1440x672.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-75x35.png 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-107x50.png 107w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-740x345.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-220x103.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective-385x180.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/18-GF-Collective.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.girlfriend.com/"></a></p>



<p>Esta es una marca que elabora ropa deportiva con materiales 100 por ciento reciclados.</p>



<p>En este sitio encontrarás textos divertidos y juguetones, como: “Girlfriend Collective elabora ropa deportiva con materiales reciclados porque la basura te luce mejor que andar contaminando el planeta”.</p>



<p>Y su eslogan combina perfectamente con su <a href="https://sleeknote.com/blog/e-commerce-value-proposition" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener">proposición de valor</a> única usando apenas tres palabras en inglés: “Ethically Made Activewear” (en español, “Ropa deportiva hecha de forma ética”).</p>



<p>Esto le hace saber instantáneamente al cliente potencial de qué se trata <a href="https://www.girlfriend.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Girlfriend Collective</a> y muestra que es posible condensar la misión, valores y filosofía de tu marca en un eslogan ultra simple.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>9. Primary Clothing: “Brilliant Basics for Babies and Kids”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="470" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-1024x470.png" alt="19 Primary" class="wp-image-112979" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-1024x470.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-300x138.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-768x352.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-1536x705.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-380x174.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-600x275.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-760x349.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-1440x661.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-109x50.png 109w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-740x339.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-220x101.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary-385x177.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/19-Primary.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.primary.com/"></a></p>



<p>Esta es otra compañía que usa la palabra “básicos” en su eslogan (en español, “Básicos brillantes para bebés y niños”).&nbsp;</p>



<p><a href="https://www.primary.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Primary Clothing</a> es una marca que se enfoca en ofrecer “ropa de calidad inesperada para niños a una fracción del precio”. Al leer su eslogan, los compradores saben que Primary Clothing es una marca específica para niños.</p>



<p>Y al usar las palabras “básicos brillantes”, los compradores saben que pueden encontrar un alto nivel de calidad, lo que ayuda a Primary Clothing a diferenciarse de competidores similares en el mercado.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Esto es algo que ellos refuerzan en su sitio web, donde explican exactamente qué es lo que los hace excelentes.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="470" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-1024x470.png" alt="20 Primary Rainbow" class="wp-image-112983" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-1024x470.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-300x138.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-768x352.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-1536x705.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-380x174.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-600x275.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-760x349.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-1440x661.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-76x35.png 76w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-109x50.png 109w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-740x339.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-220x101.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow-385x177.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/20-Primary-Rainbow.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<h2><strong>10. Sephora: “Let’s Beauty Together”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="476" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-1024x476.png" alt="21 Sephora" class="wp-image-112987" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-1024x476.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-300x140.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-768x357.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-1536x715.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-380x177.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-600x279.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-760x354.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-1440x670.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-75x35.png 75w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-107x50.png 107w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-740x344.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-220x102.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora-385x179.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/21-Sephora.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p>En mis ejemplos finales proporcionaré marcas con lemas grandiosos. Como dije antes, los lemas tienden a ser un poco más abstractos que los eslóganes y se enfocan en evocar una imagen en la mente de los compradores.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Al final, los lemas buscan principalmente ayudar a los compradores a formar asociaciones entre una frase particular y una marca. Piensa en el “Just Do It” (“Solo hazlo”) de Nike.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Por ende, es más común ver a compañías más grandes y establecidas usando lemas, porque ya tienen una cierta cantidad de equidad de marca integrada.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Uno de los mejores ejemplos es el “Let’s Beauty Together” (“Hagamos belleza juntos”) de Sephora. Esto les deja saber claramente a los compradores que la marca vende productos de belleza, y es una forma creativa de representar su actitud accesible.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Y con solo tres palabras, es corto, dulce y fácil de decir.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>11. TOMS: “We’re in Business to Improve Lives”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="498" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-1024x498.png" alt="22 TOMS" class="wp-image-112991" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-1024x498.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-768x374.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-1536x748.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-380x185.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-600x292.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-760x370.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-1440x701.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-740x360.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/22-TOMS.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.toms.com/"></a></p>



<p><a href="https://www.toms.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">TOMS</a> fue uno de los creadores del modelo de negocios “uno por uno”, en el que por cada par de zapatos comprados, regalaban un par de zapatos a alguien necesitado.</p>



<p>A medida que la marca creció con el pasar de los años cambió ligeramente ese modelo, pero su identidad de marca sigue basada fuertemente en ayudar a las personas de todo el mundo e impulsar el progreso.&nbsp;</p>



<p>El lema “We’re in business to improve lives” (“Estamos en el negocio de mejorar vidas”) es perfecto para expresar los valores de TOMS y mostrar que el cambio positivo es la fuerza motora detrás de su compañía.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Esto debería ser suficiente para despertar el interés de muchas personas y dirigirlas al sitio web de TOMS. Allí, los compradores pueden saber más sobre su misión y ver sus productos.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="496" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-1024x496.png" alt="23 TOMS CSR" class="wp-image-112995" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-1024x496.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-300x145.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-768x372.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-1536x745.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-760x368.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-1440x698.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-740x359.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/23-TOMS-CSR.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.toms.com/"></a></p>



<p>Y esto es algo en lo que te puedes inspirar e implementarlo en tu marca de e-commerce.&nbsp;</p>



<h2><strong>12. Chubbies: “The Weekend Has Arrived”</strong></h2>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="497" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-1024x497.png" alt="24 Chubbies" class="wp-image-112999" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-1024x497.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-300x146.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-768x373.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-1536x745.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-380x184.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-600x291.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-760x369.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-1440x699.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-72x35.png 72w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-103x50.png 103w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-740x359.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-220x107.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies-385x187.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/24-Chubbies.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.chubbiesshorts.com/"></a></p>



<p>Finalmente, tenemos a <a href="https://www.chubbiesshorts.com/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer noopener nofollow">Chubbies</a>, una de las marcas de ropa para hombres más “hippies” y divertidas que existen.&nbsp;</p>



<p>Ciertamente, “The weekend has arrived” (“El fin de semana ha llegado”) es uno de los lemas de e-commerce más ambiguos en el mercado. Si no conoces ya a Chubbies, probablemente no sabrías qué esperar.</p>



<p>Es por eso que esta no es, necesariamente, la mejor ruta a tomar si eres una compañía emergente que todavía está tratando de solidificar su base de clientes leales.</p>



<p>Pero si ya tienes una audiencia de tamaño considerable y buscas fortalecer tu identidad de marca, irte por esta ruta, ciertamente, tendría sentido.</p>



<p>En el caso de Chubbies, usar “El fin de semana ha llegado” conjura imágenes de diversión y emoción, lo que definitivamente va en línea con su identidad de marca.</p>



<p>Simplemente dale un vistazo a algunos de los productos “funky” que venden, como estos bañadores para hombres.</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="509" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-1024x509.png" alt="25 Chubbies Shorts" class="wp-image-113003" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-1024x509.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-300x149.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-768x382.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-1536x764.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-380x189.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-600x298.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-760x378.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-1440x716.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-70x35.png 70w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-101x50.png 101w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-740x368.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-220x109.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts-385x191.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/25-Chubbies-Shorts.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.chubbiesshorts.com/collections/best-sellers#daily-hot-deals"></a></p>



<p>Y mira algunos de sus hilarantes posts en su página de Instagram.&nbsp;</p>



<div class="wp-block-image"><figure class="aligncenter size-large"><img width="1024" height="636" src="https://sleeknote.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-1024x636.png" alt="26 Chubbies Insta" class="wp-image-113007" srcset="https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-1024x636.png 1024w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-300x186.png 300w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-768x477.png 768w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-1536x954.png 1536w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-380x236.png 380w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-600x372.png 600w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-760x472.png 760w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-1440x894.png 1440w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-56x35.png 56w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-81x50.png 81w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-740x459.png 740w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-220x137.png 220w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta-385x239.png 385w, https://n7nqziuw1z4b1r6k2adhav10-wpengine.netdna-ssl.com/wp-content/uploads/2020/11/26-Chubbies-Insta.png 1999w" sizes="(max-width: 1024px) 100vw, 1024px" /></figure></div>



<p><a href="https://www.instagram.com/chubbies/?hl=en"></a></p>



<p>Mi punto aquí es que crear un lema maravilloso requiere de un poco de sutileza y de cierta cantidad de conexión con una audiencia existente.</p>



<p>Pero Chubbies es la prueba de que sí se puede hacer cuando sigues la fórmula correcta.&nbsp;</p>


<div id="contentupgrade-block_5fa9475b96b81" class="block-content-upgrade">
    <div class="text">
        <p class="text-pretitle">RECURSOS GRATUITOS</p>
        <h2 class="text-title">¿Necesitas más inspiración para tu copywriting?</h2>
        <div class="text-content"><p>Obtén acceso a nuestro archivo swipe lleno de ejemplos de call-to-action, plantillas de email, páginas de e-commerce de alto desempeño y mucho más.</p>
